gomodel:SYNGO_5389  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1: S1PR1 was detected in synaptosomal biochemical fractions prepared from mouse cortex, with slight enrichment in the synaptosome-subfraction that excludes the active zone (membrane).. Experimental description: M&M: \"Synaptosomal fractionation was modified from Morato et al. [37]. Briefly, the mouse cortex was homogenized in 1 mL of isolation buffer ...\"\n\nantibody:\nRabbit anti-S1PR1, 1:1000 (WB)/1:500 (IFn)/1:200 (IFs), Thermofisher (PA1-40,000)" ;
